Powers.DescLong: Lore Allies have very high defense versus area of effect attacks and moderate damage resistance.
These essences are capable of Flight.
This offensive ally has less experience than a higher-level, full strength Lore pet.
This offensive ally has significantly improved combat skills, increasing their damage.
This support ally has a personal phase shield which allows them to assist you without fear of being destroyed by your enemies.
These essences are capable of Super Leaping.
